&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;今天，很多人都在传这样一条消息：&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;img class=&quot;rich_pages js_insertlocalimg&quot; data-ratio=&quot;0.329608938547486&quot; data-s=&quot;300,640&quot; data-src=&quot;http://img2.jintiankansha.me/get?src=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/RiacFDBX14xBYNd8r9VASj3HlibzLTWroBDHac1NQvNZoZFGyCwqica0Td3FH3cMk3DsVZVhNnlDoLgZsvVIaIlJw/640?wx_fmt=png&quot; data-type=&quot;png&quot; data-w=&quot;716&quot;/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;


